{"word":"G1848 - ἐξουθενέω - exouthenéō - ex-oo-then-eh'-o - Contemptible","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἐξουθενέω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">exouthenéō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">ex-oo-then-eh'-o</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Contemptible</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - அற்பமாய் எண்ணு, நிந்தி, அசட்டை பண்ணு"},{"paragraph":"to make of no account, to despise utterly"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>A variation of <a href=\"#/G1847 - ἐξουδενόω - exoudenóō - ex-oo-den-o'-o/1847\">G1847</a> and meaning the same: - contemptible, despise, least esteemed, set at nought.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}